Question [Natural]: What is the number of papers published on and after an year $Year$?

Question [Natural]: Show the papers published on and after an year $Year$
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT PaperID_Title.Title FROM PaperID_Title JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID JOIN ConfID_Venue_Year ON ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID=ConfID_PaperID.ConfID WHERE ConfID_Venue_Year.Year >= '$Year$'

Question [Natural]: Which papers were published in year $Year$?
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT PaperID_Title.Title FROM PaperID_Title JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID JOIN ConfID_Venue_Year ON ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID=ConfID_PaperID.ConfID WHERE ConfID_Venue_Year.Year='$Year$'

Question [Natural]: Give the number of papers published in the year $Year$
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT COUNT(*) FROM PaperID_Title JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID JOIN ConfID_Venue_Year ON ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID=ConfID_PaperID.ConfID WHERE ConfID_Venue_Year.Year='$Year$'

Question [Natural]: Display the ConfID of the paper with paper ID='$PaperID$'
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID FROM ConfID_Venue_Year JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.ConfID=ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID JOIN PaperID_Title ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID WHERE PaperID_Title.PaperID='$PaperID$'

Question [Natural]: In which year with paper with paper ID equals '$PaperID$' published?
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT ConfID_Venue_Year.Year FROM ConfID_Venue_Year JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.ConfID=ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID JOIN PaperID_Title ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID WHERE PaperID_Title.PaperID='$PaperID$'

Question [Natural]: What was the venue of the paper with paper ID equals '$PaperID$' published?
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT ConfID_Venue_Year.Venue FROM ConfID_Venue_Year JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.ConfID=ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID JOIN PaperID_Title ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID WHERE PaperID_Title.PaperID='$PaperID$'

Question [Natural]: What was the venue and the year of the paper with paper ID equals '$PaperID$'?
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT ConfID_Venue_Year.Venue,ConfID_Venue_Year.Year FROM ConfID_Venue_Year JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.ConfID=ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID JOIN PaperID_Title ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID WHERE PaperID_Title.PaperID='$PaperID$'

Question [Natural]: What was the year of publishing the paper '$Title$'?
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT ConfID_Venue_Year.Year FROM ConfID_Venue_Year JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.ConfID=ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID JOIN PaperID_Title ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID WHERE PaperID_Title.Title='$Title$'

Question [Natural]: What was the name of the place where paper '$Title$' published?
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT ConfID_Venue_Year.Venue FROM ConfID_Venue_Year JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.ConfID=ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID JOIN PaperID_Title ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID WHERE PaperID_Title.Title='$Title$'

Question [Natural]: Give the place and year of the paper '$Title$'
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT ConfID_Venue_Year.Venue,ConfID_Venue_Year.Year FROM ConfID_Venue_Year JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.ConfID=ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID JOIN PaperID_Title ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID WHERE PaperID_Title.Title='$Topic$'

Question [Natural]: What is the ConfID of the paper '$Title$'
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID FROM ConfID_Venue_Year JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.ConfID=ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID JOIN PaperID_Title ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID WHERE PaperID_Title.Title='$Topic$'

Question [Natural]: Display all the papers published in the year $Year$ at 'SocialNLP'
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT PaperID_Title.Title FROM PaperID_Title JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID JOIN ConfID_Venue_Year ON ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID=ConfID_PaperID.ConfID WHERE ConfID_Venue_Year.Year='$Year$' AND ConfID_Venue_Year.Venue='SocialNLP'

Question [Natural]: Give the numbers of papers published in the year $Year$ at 'SocialNLP'
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT COUNT(*) FROM PaperID_Title JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID JOIN ConfID_Venue_Year ON ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID=ConfID_PaperID.ConfID WHERE ConfID_Venue_Year.Year='$Year$' AND ConfID_Venue_Year.Venue='SocialNLP'

Question [Natural]: Display all the papers published on and after year $Year$ at 'Workshop On Parsing Technology'
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT PaperID_Title.Title FROM PaperID_Title JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID JOIN ConfID_Venue_Year ON ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID=ConfID_PaperID.ConfID WHERE ConfID_Venue_Year.Year >= '$Year$' AND ConfID_Venue_Year.Venue='Workshop On Parsing Technology'

Question [Natural]: Display all the title of the papers published after year $Year$ at 'Workshop On Parsing Technology'
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT PaperID_Title.Title FROM PaperID_Title JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID JOIN ConfID_Venue_Year ON ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID=ConfID_PaperID.ConfID WHERE ConfID_Venue_Year.Year > '$Year$' AND ConfID_Venue_Year.Venue='Workshop On Parsing Technology'

Question [Natural]: Display all the conference venue on field 'SocialNLP' in year $Year$
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT ConfID_Venue_Year.Venue FROM ConfID_Venue_Year JOIN ConfID_FieldID ON ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID=ConfID_FieldID.ConfID JOIN FieldID_Topic ON ConfID_FieldID.FieldID=FieldID_Topic.FieldID Where FieldID_Topic.Topic Like 'SocialNLP' and ConfID_Venue_Year.Year='$Year$'
